text: Isileli Tupou also known as Kaiongo Tupou (born 26 October 1984)Kaiongo Tupou player profile Scrum.com in Tofua, Tonga) is a rugby union player who plays at center. He currently plays with the Lille Métropole Rugby in the Federale 1 in France. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Tongan rugby union players Category:People from Haʻapai Category:Rugby union centres Category:Tonga international rugby union players Category:Tongan expatriate rugby union players Category:Expatriate rugby union players in France Category:Tongan expatriate sportspeople in France
